data.description: This beautifully maintained like new home is located perfectly in the up and coming area of Pensacola! There is an endless list of upgrades on this property as well. From the oversize extended rear covered porch, granite countertops in the kitchen, upgraded shelving in the laundry room, vinyl plank flooring throughout the bottom floor this home is a show stopper. Kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, granite countertops including the island, pantry, recessed LED lights, and pendant lights over the island. The half bath downstairs features a pocket door to maximize effeceincy in the space. 2 inch faux wooden blinds as window treatments in every window of the home! Upgraded light fixtures and ceiling fans throughout the home. Oversized rear covere porch with ceiling fans, and a fire pit on a large cul de sac lot. 19' x13' Master Bedroom with Large walk in Closet! A fenced in back yard with tons of room for entertaining and kids of all sizes to play! Additional concnrete was poured in the front yard to make sure there is plenty of room to park.  This home is close to all of the new growth and deverlopment in Pensacola! Come see this home before it goes!
